    In this blog, I share my tech watch mainly and sometimes I write articles 
    about things I do at work.
  </p>
  
  <h2>My projects and links</h2>
  
  <ul>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/CMarzin/cli-mr-creator" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        An npm package for creating merge request from your cli
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://corentinmarzin.fr" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        My personal and lastest folio
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://unsplash.com/@marzin_corentin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        My photography portfolio on Unsplash
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://github.com/CMarzin" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
        My Github account
      </a>
    </li>
    <li>
      <a href="https://ysf.cocommit.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
